ta/Option/Attach.lean#L29-L31","name":"Option.attach","line":29,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Attach.html#Option.attach","doc":"\"Attach\" the proof that the element of `xs`, if present, is in `xs`\nto produce a new option with the same elements but in the type `{x // x ∈ xs}`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Option/Attach.html#Option.attach\"><span class=\"name\">Option</span>.<span class=\"name\">attach</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{α : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(xs : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Subtype\">{</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Subtype\">:</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Subtype\">//</a> <span class=\"fn\">x</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\">xs</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Subtype\">}</a></span></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/93d4ae6635c0c755c9f7368f9b99483d4557b7a6/src/Init/Data/Option/Attach.lean#L21-L27","name":"Option.attachWith","line":21,"kind":"def","docLink":"./Init/Data/Option/Attach.html#Option.attachWith","doc":"\"Attach\" a proof `P x` that holds for the element of `o`, if present,\nto produce a new option with the same element but in the type `{x // P x}`. "},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Option/Attach.html#Option.attachWith\"><span class=\"nam